/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/6381e723-5008-4cd7-8b2a-78406dd04d16.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"thinking\",\n              \"thinking\": \"Now I have a full picture. Let me summarize for the Lead:\\n\\n**V4 Ecosystem Migration - Status:**\\n\\n✅ **Infrastructure (DONE):**\\n- 34 agent workspaces created\\n- Presence system (init/set/broadcast)\\n- SKILL_GATES.md for all 34 agents\\n- DEV_GATE.md for 5 key agents\\n- HANDOVER.md / FEEDBACK.md templates\\n- OPENSPEC_TRIGGER\\n- Ecosystem backup (2026-04-11)\\n- GIT_WORKFLOW.md (ecosystem standard)\\n- 17 commits ahead of origin/main (NEED PUSH)\\n\\n⚠️ **Pending Cleanup:**\\n\\n\\n- Project repos sitting in the v4-ecosystem-review workspace that should be relocated\\n- ops-manager directory partially cleaned up with remaining deleted files\\n- ahv-openclaw-setup package needs review for how it fits into the migration\\n\\nI should clarify with the Lead what they mean by \\\"plan migration\\\" — whether they're asking about the v4 infrastructure setup status or something else entirely.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"## V4 Ecosystem Migration — Status\\n\\n**Tổng quan:**\\n\\n| Hạng mục | Trạng thái |\\n|---|---|\\n| 34 agent workspaces | ✅ Hoàn tất |\\n| Presence system | ✅ Hoàn tất |\\n| SKILL_GATES / DEV_GATE | ✅ Hoàn tất |\\n| HANDOVER / FEEDBACK templates | ✅ Hoàn tất |\\n| Ecosystem backup | ✅ (2026-04-11) |\\n| GIT_WORKFLOW.md | ✅ Hoàn tất |\\n| **17 commits chưa push** | ⚠️ Cần push lên origin/main |\\n\\n**Chưa xong / Cần dọn dẹp:**\\n- Project repos (`ahv-qlhv-be`, `ahv-qlhv-fe`, `ahv-dtlx-backend`) nằm trong workspace v4-ecosystem-review — không đúng chỗ\\n- `ahv-openclaw-setup` — cần review xem có phải migration script chính thức không\\n- ops-manager: đã xóa nhưng chưa commit cleanup\\n\\n**Cần Lead xác nhận:** \\\"Plan migration\\\" ở đây là migration gì?\\n1. **V4 infrastructure** → ✅ gần xong, cần push 17 commits + dọn repo\\n2. **Migration script (ahv-openclaw-setup)** → đọc nội dung rồi báo cáo\\n3. **Khác** → nói rõ hơn\\n\\nChờ Lead hướng dẫn tiếp.\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 477,\n            \"output\": 565,\n            \"totalTokens\": 24430,\n            \"cacheRead\": 22455,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 933,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1776226552335,\n          \"responseId\": \"062e43f9b5eb94d8ca5013359b1987c9\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"6d34c150\",\n            \"seq\": 12\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:53c5832a-eecc-4d6b-a4c3-d1b78a430dca\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"unknown\",\n      \"label\": \"Cron: Daily Briefing 5AM UTC+7\",\n      \"displayName\": \"Cron: Daily Briefing 5AM UTC+7\",\n      \"updatedAt\": 1776208566543,\n      \"sessionId\": \"26f7c499-7fac-499e-bf9f-921a2e2ab1b6\",\n      \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 21354,\n      \"estimatedCostUsd\": 0,\n      \"systemSent\": true,\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/26f7c499-7fac-499e-bf9f-921a2e2ab1b6.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"thinking\",\n\n⚠️ [... middle content omitted — showing head and tail ...]\n\nidation\\n   - Uses encrypted data for FE attendance\\n\\n4. **Checkins module:**\\n   - Good separation between Schedule and Abnormal checkin\\n   - validateCreatorInParticipants is a private method\\n   - Good validation of time constraints\\n   - Overall clean architecture\\n\\n5. **OKRs module:**\\n   - Extremely complex aggregation pipeline in getOKRByFilter - lots of nested logic\\n   - No DRY violations detected\\n   - Good RBAC\\n\\n6. **Leave Requests module:**\\n   - 656 lines in leaveRequests.service.ts - VERY LARGE\\n   - Two-level approval workflow (Manager + HR)\\n   - Good leave balance management\\n   - Good notification system\\n   - Some DRY issues: repeated employee lookup, approval logic patterns\\n\\n7. **Auth module:**\\n   - Good token management (access + refresh)\\n   - Cookie-based refresh token\\n   - Solid implementation overall\\n\\n8. **Roles/Permissions module:**\\n   - Proper use of transactions for consistency\\n   - Redis caching for permissions with cache-busting on updates\\n   - Service instantiates itself with PermissionService.callingPermissionMaps preventing race conditions\\n\\n9. **Niko modules:**\\n   - Emotion: Good service\\n\\n, well-structured\\n   - Orders: Uses transactions properly for complex operations\\n   - Wallets: Good balance tracking\\n   - Criteria: Has try-catch with generic error rethrow - not ideal\\n   - Gifts: Good but has hardcoded 'PENDING' string (magic number)\\n   - Cart: Clean service\\n\\n**FE (React/TypeScript/RTK Query):**\\n\\n1. **API files:**\\n   - Good use of RTK Query with providesTags/invalidatesTags\\n   - Some use of `any` types (attendanceApi, okrApi, leaveApi)\\n   - Proper use of overrideExisting\\n\\n2. **AccountPage.tsx:**\\n   - 413 lines - reasonable size\\n   - Good separation of concerns with multiple forms\\n   - Clean TypeScript usage\\n   - No loading states, error handling, or prop drilling issues\\n\\n3. **EmployeePage.tsx:**\\n   - 311 lines - reasonable size\\n   - Clean patterns with hooks like usePermission, AccessControl\\n   - Good use of memoization\\n\\n4. **NikoPage.tsx:**\\n   - 779 lines - VERY LARGE, should be split into sub-components\\n   - Hardcoded emotion data in component (should be from API)\\n   - EMOTION_MAP created in render body\\n\\nNow I'm identifying the critical issues. The attendance module has massive code duplication across multiple files, the leaveRequests service is oversized at 656 lines, and there are hardcoded magic strings scattered throughout. The NikoPage component at 779 lines needs refactoring into smaller pieces. Beyond that, I'm seeing `any` types leaking across the FE API files, missing JSDoc comments in most places, and inconsistent error handling with empty catch blocks in some niko services. There's also mixed language usage between Vietnamese and English that should be standardized, and some files have unnecessary complexity that could be simplified.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"Now I have enough data to write the comprehensive code quality report. Let me create it:\\n\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n              \"id\": \"call_function_4mi0q9it66m6_1\",\n              \"name\": \"exec\",\n              \"arguments\": {\n                \"command\": \"mkdir -p /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/reviews\"\n              }\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 5824,\n            \"output\": 924,\n            \"totalTokens\": 101731,\n            \"cacheRead\": 89378,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 5605,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1775982347614,\n          \"responseId\": \"062a8a0d36758ec7975bb77b6a44b7d6\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"3f484677\",\n            \"seq\": 136\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    }\n  ]\n}[... 82959 more characters truncated]"}],"details":{"count":39,"sessions":[{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:6f3323ef-607e-42a0-b946-611913081d31","kind":"other","channel":"webchat","origin":{"provider":"heartbeat"},"label":"Cron: 5p Progress Report - DTLX","displayName":"webchat:g-agent-master-orchestrator-cron-6f3323ef-607e-42a0-b946-611913081d31","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat"},"updatedAt":1776235521181,"sessionId":"935cac44-6ed1-4741-871b-cb05591f34b7","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":34743,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"running","startedAt":1776235520697,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/935cac44-6ed1-4741-871b-cb05591f34b7.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:6f3323ef-607e-42a0-b946-611913081d31 5p Progress Report — AHV DTLX/QLHV] You are the 5-minute change-detecting reporter for the AHV DTLX (Đào Tạo Lái Xe) ecosystem.\n\nCheck sessions_list. Compare current active sessions against the last known state stored in memory/heartbeat-state.json.\n\n**If nothing has changed since the last report:**\n- Stay SILENT. Send nothing. Not even HEARTBEAT_OK. Just exit quietly.\n\n**If there IS a change** (new session spawned, session died, agent failed, task started/completed, blocker appeared), compose a concise change report to group -5163901258:\n\nFormat:\n🟡 Orbis-DTLX — 5p Update | {HH:MM} UTC {DD MMM}\n\nChanges detected:\n• [list of actual changes]\n\nPipeline: {HEALTHY if no failures / DEGRADED if failures}\n• Active sessions: N\n• MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\n\nOnly send when something changed. Stay silent when stable.\nCurrent time: Wednesday, April 15th, 2026 - 6:44 AM (UTC) / 2026-04-15 06:44 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1776235520697,"__openclaw":{"id":"4d9c2279","seq":1}},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me check the sessions list and compare against the stored state in memory/heartbeat-state.json."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_m9cigv7vbzhy_1","name":"sessions_list","arguments":{"messageLimit":2}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_m9cigv7vbzhy_2","name":"memory_get","arguments":{"path":"heartbeat-state.json","corpus":"memory"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":430,"output":82,"totalTokens":14456,"cacheRead":13944,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776235520857,"responseId":"062e67022e06f75046dffe6d8b4d6225","__openclaw":{"id":"04992cdf","seq":2}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","kind":"other","channel":"telegram","origin":{"provider":"telegram","accountId":"main_bot"},"displayName":"telegram:g-agent-master-orchestrator-telegram-direct-6053576134","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram","to":"telegram:6053576134","accountId":"main_bot"},"updatedAt":1776235450235,"sessionId":"8e18daec-1780-455f-b7c4-896849ef86be","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":75214,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"running","startedAt":1776235399004,"childSessions":["agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:8d8e1952-016d-4c2d-819c-c3b32e3b45b2","agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:cd3256cb-3b94-49db-84de-ab99c44cf2fd","agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:aa7da6a2-9c14-4261-b1b7-936fb3c60ec8","agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:53ffecba-7a14-43e4-91be-9b3efcc56072","agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:5d2b77de-dd66-41c2-b053-30aabd324a0e","agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:8bffa95f-1686-4571-a0ed-e69d265eb964"],"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"telegram","lastTo":"telegram:6053576134","lastAccountId":"main_bot","transcriptPath":"/root/.opencla