: HEALTHY ✅\n• Active sessions: 2 (DTLX 5p ✅ Agent Status to Lead ✅)\n• MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\n• Cron: 5p progress ✅ | Daily @ 5AM+7 ✅\n• Blockers: cron:ac986a8d orphan (~44h) | cron:b653a6c0 orphan (~39h) — low priority\n\n— Orbis 🌐"}],"timestamp":1776230031335,"provenance":{"kind":"inter_session","sourceSessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:6f3323ef-607e-42a0-b946-611913081d31","sourceChannel":"telegram","sourceTool":"sessions_send"},"__openclaw":{"id":"7e931fe2","seq":1245}},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Skip."},{"type":"text","text":"\nHEARTBEAT_OK"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776230031527,"responseId":"062e5191759184ba1748931eed3e4ec0","__openclaw":{"id":"61aed5b7","seq":1246}},{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🟡 Orbis — 5p Update | 05:18 UTC 15 Apr\n\nChanges detected:\n• 🔄 QLHV 5p Monitor (cron:ed2d0b5d) — cycled normally, new instance running since ~05:13 UTC ✅\n• ✅ Child subagents from previous cycle — all completed normally (no failures)\n\nPipeline: HEALTHY ✅\n• Active sessions: 3 (QLHV 5p ✅ DTLX 5p ✅ Agent Status ✅)\n• MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\n• Cron: 5p progress ✅ | Daily @ 5AM+7 ✅\n• Blockers: cron:ac986a8d orphan (~44h) | cron:b653a6c0 orphan (~39h) — low priority\n\n— Orbis 🌐"}],"timestamp":1776230479540,"provenance":{"kind":"inter_session","sourceSessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7","sourceChannel":"telegram","sourceTool":"sessions_send"},"__openclaw":{"id":"b3b51c71","seq":1247}},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Another heartbeat. Ack."},{"type":"text","text":"HEARTBEAT_OK"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776230479735,"responseId":"062e535265c30c7f2211a1ec73553a10","__openclaw":{"id":"9f731a62","seq":1248}}],"truncated":true,"droppedMess